    "default_locale": "en-US",
    "description": {
        "en-US": "  - To lock the text, highlight any part of the text then select 'Lock'\n  - To unlock text, highlight the text (including the --BEGIN/END LOCKTHETEXT-- markers), then select 'Unlock'\n  - Focus your cursor in an input/textarea field without any selection, then select 'Lock' will lock all your editing text\n  - Locked text can only be unlocked with the same passphrase which is used to lock the text\n  - If you selection is in an input/textarea field, locked/unlocked text will replace your selection\n  - If you selection is not in an input/textarea field (e.g. html email body or rich format doc), locked/unlocked text will display in a new window\n"
    },
    "developer_comments": {
        "en-US": "Please email your question to Lock The Text users mailing list (lockthetext-users@lists.sourceforge.net).\nThis extension is still in beta and you are welcome to contact me directly by email (mail2arthur@gmail.com)."
